data.enText: the designing, building and flying of aircraft

simple_means.memory_skill: avi 鸟 + ation 行为 → 像鸟〔在空中飞〕→ 飞行

example: air travel involves too much waiting in airports
if you've time to spare go by air

tr: the operation of aircraft to provide transportation
the aggregation of a country's military aircraft

value.def: Aviation is the operation and production of aircraft.

partsOfSpeech.dec: avar 渴望 + ice 表性质 → 贪心
avaric〔e〕贪心 + ious …的 → 贪婪的，贪心的
av 渴望 + id …的 → 渴望的；贪婪的
avid 渴望的；贪婪的 + ity 具备某种性质，状况 → 贪婪
avi 鸟 + ary 场所 →〔养〕鸟的地方 → 鸟舍
avi 鸟 + ation 行为，过程，状态，结果 → 像鸟〔在空中飞〕→ 飞行
avi 鸟 + ator 表人 → 像鸟一样飞翔的人 → 飞行员
avi 鸟 + culture 培养 → 养鸟业
